- Perform sled and arena testing to assess enhanced effectiveness of upscaled weapons against hardened targets to include
effectiveness on tunnels.
- Demonstrate proof of ejection system dart survivability for the Command, Control and Communications for Penetrating Ordnance
(C3PO) project, an effort developing a novel capability to deny an adversary access to/from their tunnel facilities using current
penetrating weapons.
- Develop WMD electronic attack capabilities to destroy, degrade, and/or disrupt WMD adjacent Command, Control, Computing,
Communications, Cyber, Intelligence, Surveillance, Reconnaissance, and Targeting (C5ISRT) components.
