commonality and joint programs with focus on interoperability, communications, navigation, Joint Services
avionics obsolescence management, and update of the Core Avionics Master Plan.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
Provide leadership and staff to support Naval Aviation interaction with and contributions to the JSRC-AS that
promote commonality and interoperability in Avionics solutions. The Navy team also captures and reflects these
alignments in the (Naval Aviation) Core Avionics Master Plan.
