the President's Department of Government Efficiency Workforce Optimization Initiative.”

The FY26 request for 0605898F has a net reduction of $0.331 million. The overall reductions included $0.621 million decrease of workforce optimization, and a $0.952
million increase for updated average work year costs to account for changes in economic assumptions, awards, benefits, and workforce mixes. The average work year
cost increase allows for full funding of the programmed full-time equivalents to ensure the Air Force has the most qualified individuals to remain competitive and lethal.

