up the roles of care, and return warfighters to the fight, especially in the Distributed Maritime environment. Each work unit undertaken in this program has a military
requirement. Efforts are justified based upon military payoff and cost benefit. There is a strong potential for dual use, technology transfer, and biotechnology firms/
industry participation in the projects.

