 (formerly the AF CMP thrust), Access (formerly the Access/Infrastructure thrust), and Cyber Weapons (formerly the Payloads thrust) OCO-related product lines as
 subsystems and technical enablers that will each consist of the Off Network, Telephony Network, and Infrastructure mission thread portfolios. NOTE. Payloads will be
