A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Mission Partner Environment (MPE) enables secure sharing of operational information for collaboration between and among the United States (US) and mission
partners to include federal, State, local, tribal agencies, allies, coalition members, host nations, other nations, US and international Non-Governmental Organizations,
multinational treaty organizations, and private sector organizations. RDT&E required to continue development, integration, and testing of capabilities to support US and
mission partners.

