       Change Summary Explanation
       Change is due to the transfer of responsibilities for Mission Partner Environment (MPE) operations, sustainment, and development activities from the United
       States Air Force to Department of War CIO and the Defense Information System Agency. In FY27, the Mission Partner Environment (MPE) portfolio will provide
       the foundational technology and support that enables the DoW to effectively collaborate and interoperate with mission partners across all phases of operations.
       Continued investment in MPE is essential to ensure combined Command and Control (C2) of coalition forces, secure information sharing, and the effective use of
       US and Partner nation military power in an increasingly complex and contested global security environment.




